summary: This document is an evidence custody record from the U.S. Department of Justice Office of the Inspector General, detailing the seizure of property on May 15, 2022, from a location in Palm Beach, Florida. It includes chain of custody logs and associated FBI property receipts, indicating formal evidence handling procedures.

events.title: Property Seizure
events.description: Seizure of property from a location in Palm Beach, Florida, documented by the Office of the Inspector General.

keyFacts: Evidence was seized on May 15, 2022, from a location in Palm Beach, Florida.
The document is an official evidence custody record from the U.S. Department of Justice Office of the Inspector General.
Chain of custody logs show evidence handling on dates including October 14, 2022, and December 19, 2022.
Associated FBI property receipts (FD-597 forms) indicate evidence was received and processed by the FBI.
The document references case IDs and log numbers, indicating it is part of a formal investigative process.
